<!-- Categories go here and interwikis go in Wikidata. -->
[[Category:Cross-reference templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]
[[Category:Wikipedia page-section templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]
[[Category:Hatnote templates]]
}}</includeonly>

